Introduction

GIRLKIND XJR (걸카인드 XJR) was a two-member sub-unit of the girl group GIRLKIND consisting of JK and Seheun under Nextlevel Entertainment. They made their official debut on August 29, 2019 with the mini album "Life is Diamond". On August 13, 2022, Nextlevel Entertainment announced that the group has disbanded after a long period of discussion, because of internal issues.
